//  Updated: Unreal (MontuZ@Gmail.com)
//  Added: The 4 const's below.. MAGIC_LEVELMULTI, MAGIC_CHANCEMULTI, NPC_STAT_MULTIPLIER & SKILL_STAT_CAP.
//  If you want overall better loot from monsters.
//  Set MAGIC_LEVELMULTI above 1.0. Example, 1.25.
//  If you want lower loot from monsters.
//  Set MAGIC_LEVELMULTI below 1.0. Example, 0.75.
//  Same goes for MAGIC_CHANCEMULTI. If you want more of a chance to get magic items, set it above
//  1.0.
//
//  HIT/STAM/MANA is NOT used anymore to determain a NPC's max life/mana/stam.
//  NPC_STAT_MULTIPLIER * Npc's Str/Int/Dex == Max Life/Mana/Stam.
//
//  I added this to make it easier for us all. So we don't have to go through the npcdesc.cfg
//  and set all the levels to what we want.
//
//  1.0 is like 100% normal; so 1.25 is 125% (+25% more than normal)
//
//  NOTE: Default Setting for ALL of these Consts is 1.0;
//  Don't forget if you change these you'll need to compile everything.
//
// Start - These consts make a big differance in-game!
